response.overview: Upon making a life altering decision, Jabari Keating (Darius "Nastyelgic" Jackson), is a candid first person narrative film that explores his personal reflections, life experiences and trials and tribulations as an African American in present day America.
response.tagline: Exploring Jabari Keating's trials and tribulations as an African American in present-day America.
response.title: Jabari Keating
